Build command:

```bash
cd /home/zar/claude/lean-projects/mettapedia
ulimit -Sv 6291456 && export LAKE_JOBS=3 && nice -n 19 \
  lake build Mettapedia.Logic.PLNIntensionalRegression
```
-/

